These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
House: townhouse, gothic-revival
2 different pets are kept: mouse, dog
The people have 2 different jobs:  writer, accountant
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the writer##1
2. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| House   | gothic-revival    | townhouse |
| Pet         | dog | mouse    |
| Job     | writer     | accountant      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: watermelon, pomegranate
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, parkour
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, aquamarine
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Food      | pomegranate  | watermelon   |
| Sport   | parkour | volleyball  |
| Color     | aquamarine   | amber |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, chinese
The people have 2 different jobs:  photographer, journalist
2 different games are played: scrabble, monopoly
1. the chinese is in an even position##4
2. the photographer is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Nationality         | colombian   | chinese  |
| Job   | journalist | photographer  |
| Game         | scrabble   | monopoly |

