.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, fanta
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, biathlon
City: miami, colone
1. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Beverage          | tea | fanta |
| Sport   | biathlon   | skiing   |
| City     | colone       | miami      |

