.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: pink, coral
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: scientific, spy
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
3. the person who likes pink is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Color    | coral | pink     |
| Beverage     | water | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | scientific    |

 #################################

 
