.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-11::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, skiing
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, november
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, cherry
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Sport           | skiing     | biathlon |
| Birthday   | november | june  |
| Food     | cherry      | eggplant |

