.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, software-developer
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, bus
There 2 different types of food: avocado, mango
1. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
3. the doctor is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Job         | software-developer | doctor |
| Transport   | scooter     | bus     |
| Food           | mango          | avocado     |

