.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-20::.
City: paris, venice
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, magic-tricks
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, marigold
1. the person traveling to paris is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| City   | paris | venice |
| Hobby   | chess  | magic-tricks  |
| Flower     | marigold | daisy    |

 